{"tid":766314,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得幾條友計劃搞大單嘢嘅過程好刺激？","createTime":"2018-08-03T13:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T14:10:08.000Z","uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"605b1e7e71196628b511894ec0c1856c2f9f39cb","tid":766314,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"純討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩過GTA V payday嘅巴絲可能知我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四 五條友計劃一單大茶飯 唔知打劫邊間大銀行 大金行 <br />\n<br />\n要預早幾個月 日以繼夜 夜以繼日觀察目標附近環境嘅變化 <br />\n<br />\n要深入目標地點 記錄所需嘅資料 例如電機房位置 cam嘅位置 等等<br />\n<br />\n又要知道當目標發生突發事會點處理 等我地提早應變<br />\n<br />\n分派工作 崗位 額外請車手 槍手等等支援<br />\n<br />\n最後係計劃好逃走路線 逃走車輛同後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到實際行動嘅時候就另一個刺激嘅層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有計劃咁去搞單大嘢 好過魯莽搶劫 成功率同逃跑率都高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4334b693cfb17d5791345295fbb28733775a1c95","tid":766314,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695b2cec5f8bc03e8d2b74f74960d78411a55011","tid":766314,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c4b1f75fce7f801ab2e9c347ff0e0ccdfe6f06","tid":766314,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"695b2cec5f8bc03e8d2b74f74960d78411a55011","tid":766314,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"純討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95325fb6a8270b337643d787ac